moduleMetadataJson.name: Ubiquiti Configuration Importer
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module imports an Ubiquiti device configuration.
        The db file within the .unf backup is the data file for
        Unifi. This module can take either the db file or .unf.
author: h00die

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.description: The target host(s), range CIDR identifier, or hosts file with syntax 'file:<path>'
